OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,FPlans for a national day to honour
OL,7,Fvictims and survivors of terror
OL,8,Fattacks have been announced as part of
OL,9,FGovernment efforts to boost support
OL,10,Ffor those affected by terrorism.
OL,12,FViews are being sought over the move
OL,13,Ffrom victims, survivors and the public
OL,14,Fon what the day would be called, ways
OL,15,Ffor victims to be commemorated and a
OL,16,Fdate for the event.
