OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,FA 12-week consultation launched on
OL,7,FWednesday comes after survivors of
OL,8,Fterror attacks have campaigned for
OL,9,Fmore recognition and support for those
OL,10,Faffected by atrocities.
OL,12,FThe Government has also announced
OL,13,Fplans to set up a new support hub to
OL,14,Fhelp victims in the immediate and long-
OL,15,Fterm aftermath of terror attacks.
OL,17,FSupport network Survivors Against
OL,18,FTerror (SAT) co-founder Brendan Cox
OL,19,Fsaid: "Survivors of terror attacks
OL,20,Fhave been crying out for change for
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
