OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,F"Today's double announcement is a
OL,7,Fmajor step forward in giving survivors
OL,8,Fand victims the recognition they
OL,9,Fdeserve and the support that they need.
OL,11,F"Terrorists aim to divide and weaken
OL,12,Four society - our best response is to
OL,13,Fhold together - and stage one of that
OL,14,Fis looking after those who have
OL,15,Fsuffered the most."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
