OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,FSurvivor of the Westminster Bridge
OL,7,Fattack in 2017, Travis Frain, who has
OL,8,Fcampaigned for a national day, also
OL,9,Fwelcomed the move as remembrance and
OL,10,Frecognition are "key to building
OL,11,Fsocietal resilience against violent
OL,13,Fextremism".
OL,15,FHe added: "I'm pleased to see that
OL,16,Fthis government recognises the
OL,17,Fimportance of these issues and the
OL,18,Frole that they can play in
OL,19,Ffacilitating the recovery of those
OL,20,Fimpacted by horrific acts of
OL,21,Fterrorism."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
