OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,FOther recommendations from the review
OL,7,Finclude better communication with
OL,8,Fvictims to raise awareness of the
OL,9,Fsupport offered to them, and for
OL,10,Fimproved support for children and
OL,11,Fyoung people.
OL,13,FSecurity minister Dan Jarvis said:
OL,14,F"The impact of a terrorist attack is
OL,15,Flong-lasting and evolving. Victims and
OL,16,Fsurvivors of terrorism need the
OL,17,Fhighest levels of support to recover
OL,18,Fand rebuild their lives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
