OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,F"These reforms will significantly
OL,7,Fenhance the support available to those
OL,8,Faffected.
OL,10,F"I would like to pay tribute to the
OL,11,Fbravery and courage of all those who
OL,12,Fhelped to shape these reforms and
OL,13,Fpledge my commitment to ensuring
OL,14,Fvictims and survivors of terrorism
OL,15,Freceive the support and recognition
OL,16,Fthey deserve."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
