OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,FThe support hub, which will aim to
OL,7,Fstreamline services for victims, is
OL,8,Fexpected to be established next year
OL,9,Fafter a procurement process has taken
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,FDetails of how the hub will run are
OL,13,Fyet to be confirmed following that
OL,14,Fprocess.
OL,16,FCheryl Stollery, wife of John Stollery
OL,17,Fwho was killed in the terror attack in
OL,18,FSousse, Tunisia in 2015, said she
OL,19,Fbacked the support hub to empower
OL,20,Fsurvivors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
