OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,F"I believe it will be a cornerstone
OL,7,Ffor the future in being able to
OL,8,Fempower survivors to regain hope,
OL,9,Fstrength and resilience, not just in
OL,10,Fthe weeks after the incident but also
OL,11,Ffor the long term as needed," she said.
OL,13,FDr Cath Hill, who survived the
OL,14,FManchester Arena bombing in 2017,
OL,15,Fadded: "If we are to combat the
OL,16,Fdevastation that terrorism can cause,
OL,17,Fas a society, we must care for those
OL,18,Fwho bear the brunt of these acts of
OL,19,Fterror."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
