OL,3,CPlans for a special day to honour
OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,FThe announcement comes as a proposed
OL,7,Flaw that aims to help prevent and
OL,8,Freduce the harm of terror attacks at
OL,9,Fevent venues after the Manchester
OL,10,Farena attack continues through
OL,11,FParliament.
OL,13,FKnown as Martyn's Law, it will compel
OL,14,Fall UK venues that expect 200 or more
OL,15,Fpeople to be on-site to prepare for
OL,16,Fthe event of a terror attack, such as
OL,17,Festablishing evacuation plans.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
