OL,4,Cvictims and survivors of terror attacks
OL,6,FFigen Murray campaigned for the law
OL,7,Fchange after her 29-year-old son
OL,8,FMartyn Hett was killed, with 21 other
OL,9,Fpeople, in the Manchester Arena
OL,10,Fbombing at the end of an Ariana Grande
OL,11,Fconcert in May 2017.
OL,13,FA review into the Government's
OL,14,FCriminal Injuries Compensation
OL,15,FAuthority (CICA) first undertaken
OL,16,Funder the previous government is also
OL,17,Fbeing considered by ministers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
